        "subject": "LU-37 create proper macro check for bdi interface",
        "message": "LU-37 create proper macro check for bdi interface\n\nThe original patch by Lai Siyao from bz 23064 was landed in Lustre 1.8.\nThis is a rebase against 2.1.\n\nThe wb_cnt field of struct backing_dev_info is removed by patches\nbackported to RHEL6 kernels from 2.6.34.  Replace Lustre autoconf\ntests for wb_cnt with explicit checks for bdi_register() and the s_bdi\nfield since those symbols are what the code actually references.\n\nChange-Id: I6895903b4f54045d0d5f28fd0bd76f158340f918\nSigned-off-by: Ned Bass <bass6@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
